  <div class="comment_text">I went to Spain as a teenager and saw Guernica in person. It was the first painting to ever really have an effect on me. It&#x27;s stunning. A perfect example of how art can transmit a message between people across time and space, I just knew that I was feeling how Picasso wanted me to feel.<p>If you have the chance to see this painting you should, no website can do it justice (although this is a very nice try).</div>
